To complete the implementation:

Install dependencies:

bashCopynpm install express mongoose dotenv express-validator react-helmet lucide-react @tailwindcss/forms jsonwebtoken cors

Create a .env file in the root directory:

CopyMONGODB_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key
PORT=3000

Set up the build process in your package.json:

jsonCopy{
  "scripts": {
    "start": "node server/index.js",
    "dev": "nodemon server/index.js",
    "client": "cd client && npm start",
    "build": "cd client && npm run build",
    "dev:full": "concurrently \"npm run dev\" \"npm run client\""
  }
}

Initialize and configure Tailwind CSS for styling.
Set up proper security measures:


Add CORS configuration
Implement rate limiting
Set up proper environment variables
Add input sanitization
Implement proper error handling
